				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Thematically, this VB is a conversation about the goblin camp and how difficult it might be to find the druid there. Player will be aware that he's being held captive somewhere in the camp and can see the goblins's strength.\r\n\r\nThis occurs over walking into a trigger, so lines between speaker 1 and speaker 2 can be fairly opinionated."
